  "reference_number": "RUS3177",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State has reasonable grounds to suspect GIMLI TRADE LLC-FZ is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis that it is and has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia through: (1) carrying on business of economic significance to the Government of Russia; (2) providing financial services, or making available funds, economic resources, goods or technology, to a person who is involved in obtaining a benefit from of supporting the Government of Russia within the meaning of regulation 6(4)(a) to (e), namely A7 LLC. \n",
